      "description": "$46,900 - Mint-condition example that presents beautifully inside and out and appears exceptionally well kept. This is the kind of car a buyer can expect to be clean, complete, and properly sorted, with excellent cosmetics, a very tidy interior, and the overall feel of a top-tier car rather than a project or average driver. It should make an outstanding turnkey example for someone who wants one of the best-condition cars on the market.",
