    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older fair-condition car that appears complete and usable, but it shows clear age, wear, and cosmetic imperfections throughout. Paint, trim, and interior present as driver-quality with visible flaws, and buyers should expect the kind of ongoing maintenance, refreshing, and small repairs typical of a car in this condition. It should suit someone looking for an affordable entry point or a solid project to improve over time rather than a fully sorted showpiece.",
