    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a buyer who values affordability above all else. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking basic transportation, a project, or a low-cost extra vehicle. Priced to reflect its current condition while still delivering solid value for the money, this is a straightforward, no-nonsense option for the right buyer.",
