      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, honest option for someone who wants cheap transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced to reflect the wear, and for the money it offers a great chance to get on the road without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re realistic and want something budget-friendly with potential, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Honest driver/project with solid old-school appeal and straightforward mechanicals. This one shows its age cosmetically, but it fires up, moves under its own power, and offers a good foundation for someone who wants an inexpensive commuter, shop truck, or weekend fix-up. The powertrain feels like a usable core, with the kind of simplicity that makes maintenance approachable. Not a showpiece, but a budget-friendly rig with parts/repair upside for the right buyer. Priced to reflect condition and sold as-is.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
