      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with unmistakable personality, this car has the kind of road presence and old-school charm that turns a simple drive into a story. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who sees possibility where others see patina\u2014a rewarding project, a dependable stopgap, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with character to spare. If you\u2019ve been looking for an affordable car with soul and plenty of potential, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
